# LAN dev: keep unset so axios hits same-origin /api/v1 (Vite → :8002).
# Do not point at another host's http://localhost:8002 — CSRF uses the page Origin.
#
# If http://localhost:3001 fails but http://<LAN-IP>:3001 works on the dev machine,
# use http://127.0.0.1:3001 (IPv4 loopback) or ensure Vite listens on :: (vite.config.ts).
# From another device, never use localhost — use the server's IP or domain.


# Media files are served from the same origin as the SPA (via Vite proxy in
# dev). Don't set VITE_MEDIA_BASE_URL — cross-origin media breaks cookie auth
# and the iframe preview (X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN).
